{"tid":2034302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭文貴 : 「香港自貿區地位一定會被取消」 巴斯：恐重演97年亞洲金融風暴","createTime":"2020-05-25T07:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T00:54:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"111e4a680ce7a45b30285b1ab61c9ca68a881b25","tid":2034302,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"中國政府決定在5月28日表決通過「香港國安法」，香港恆生指數在5月22日跌了一千多點，本周第一個交易日（25日）開盤就重挫380點。流亡美國的中國富豪郭文貴爆料，北京持續護盤，子彈有點緊了，但「香港自貿區地位一定會被取消」。海曼資本投資長凱爾巴斯則對《CNN》說，國安法引起香港資金外逃，恐引發第二次東南亞金融風暴。<br />\n<br />\n上周北京兩會宣布要推動《香港國安法》引起全球譁然，香港居民再度湧上街頭抗議，港股大跌。郭文貴3年前曾提過、去年再度重申「香港自貿區地位一定會被取消」。他透露，現在北京當局正和西方國家私底下談判，想保障自己海外子女、私生子女以及資產；同時，在香港的北京高官家人，也急著帶錢連夜撤離，逃往紐西蘭、日本，他們認為對北京仍友善的國家。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，香港的外資加速撤離，海曼資本管理（Hayman Capital Management）創辦人凱爾巴斯（Kyle Bass）研判，「香港自貿區地位一定會被取消」，他在台北時間24日接受美國有線電視新聞《CNN》主播Julia Chatterley連線採訪時表示，他擔心這波香港事件重演1997年的亞洲金融風暴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E8%B2%BF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D-%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%83%E8%A2%AB%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E5%87%B1%E7%88%BE%E5%B7%B4%E6%96%AF-%E6%81%90%E9%87%8D%E6%BC%9497%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4-063232024.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588-%25E5%2587%25B1%25E7%2588%25BE%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%2596%25AF-%25E6%2581%2590%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%25BC%259497%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%259A%25B4-063232024.html&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3jcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=1609ada3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E8%B2%BF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D-%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%83%E8%A2%AB%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E5%87%B1%E7%88%BE%E5%B7%B4%E6%96%AF-%E6%81%90%E9%87%8D%E6%BC%9497%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4-063232024.html</a>"},{"pid":"7de8447031b34c639b329508e4d1e512df97f153","tid":2034302,"uid":85659,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:10:35.000Z","msg":"新燈神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b618fa7bbac586af55786e9444838ed32b5996","tid":2034302,"uid":32028,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"佢真係無一次中過, 係咪?"},{"pid":"f25537fd7a2ad82f35343fc1eaea5220934bdb9e","tid":2034302,"uid":161374,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:12:11.000Z","msg":"佢講完姐係唔會取消"},{"pid":"de06eb1535604ec85a3eae79a20f80bf95ef2463","tid":2034302,"uid":60434,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:13:38.000Z","msg":"啫係冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc9779b3912f18e465705bf536cb9e2bab9fada","tid":2034302,"uid":271199,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:14:27.000Z","msg":"等睇佢話64支共滅亡，如果唔準，就咪撚post呢條9up王"},{"pid":"cf124c9149e77ac82d98129311847f59b7bc33cc","tid":2034302,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"de06eb1535604ec85a3eae79a20f80bf95ef2463","tid":2034302,"uid":60434,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:13:38.000Z","msg":"啫係冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:15:36.000Z","msg":"跨國人口販賣"},{"pid":"871a2aac1770439da3c873f8d7f88859377bba8c","tid":2034302,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5WYgbm4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5WYgbm4.jpg&h=afb6a337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳送門 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.citizenspc.org/survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org%2Fsurvey&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3jcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=fef6b6ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.citizenspc.org/survey</a>"},{"pid":"bc93e9023ea63a6e0c68e58443e2b7289efd54a3","tid":2034302,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:21:22.000Z","msg":"冰片又冇 同游膠源同級既鳩up佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9195e889a3e44470ecc2578a7a4faea06434f55","tid":2034302,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"郭文貴：中共過埋2020年仲未收皮我就跳樓死！<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3jcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=769000c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&h=4b21dc27\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2019-01-04 16:32:40</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/06/4kDjBt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F12%2F06%2F4kDjBt.png&h=2d3a0463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n一直預告西方世界將與中國全面對抗的郭文貴還強調：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2020年是結束共產黨在中國的最後一年，否則文貴就從那18樓跳下去，大家要記住我的承諾。</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴又爆料：中共將於今年6/4滅亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3jcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=5ae01c31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&h=2b44cc57\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">2020-02-18 01:35:08</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/18/phpkwmUEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2FphpkwmUEi.jpg&h=81372548&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n流亡美國的中國富商郭文貴不定時暴露中國高層黑幕，2月15日在直播中又爆料，共產黨推行的中國夢已經完全不可能實現，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今年6月4日「沒有共產黨的新中國一定會成立」，屆時會由世界上許多國家共同宣布。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a4e077f5f6b62d3c29eef57a13e1871d498d54a3","tid":2034302,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bc93e9023ea63a6e0c68e58443e2b7289efd54a3","tid":2034302,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:21:22.000Z","msg":"冰片又冇 同游膠源同級既鳩up佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"利申睇過"},{"pid":"9359627ca38e09e44bdca16bbc0e6553eab3897b","tid":2034302,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:24:22.000Z","msg":"如果佢同蕭生各講一邊會點？矛盾"},{"pid":"31e0edd3dd4707599b1b04d476d02928e5c53b80","tid":2034302,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27a511b6bdf02beadd40eac5eb26f98b2d2df531","tid":2034302,"uid":151903,"like":0,"dislike"